message: Here are some highlights of our panel. We cannot begin to express how grateful we are to Ryan Anderson Bell, the founder of SummitLive for inviting us to this incredible event!  The crowd that continued to pour in was such an encouragement in this battle.  Thank you so much to all who attended, participated and shared what they've learned.  This is one of those fights where knowledge truly is power!
